red cod
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:<i>Pseudophycis bachus</i> (also listed as <i>Physiculus bac(c)hus, </i> and in early texts <i>Lotella bacchus</i>), fam Moridae, an often abundant food fish of mainly SI waters; .in early writings under a listing <i>Lotella bacchus,</i> occas. and confusingly referred to as rock cod or yellowtail qqv.
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: Contrast bastard red cod.
